{
  "stem": "15174.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We sent-- I remember, we sent a telegram to President Roosevelt and Mrs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Roosevelt.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember people talking about this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The only response from President Roosevelt was he sent out a PT boat to make sure that nobody jumped overboard and tried to sail to-- try to swim to Florida.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So that was not-- not successful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We made representations and Jewish organizations also made representations to the Canadian government who said that they said no and of course all representations were also made to the other Central American and I believe South American governments to nobodies they all said no we were not interested we have enough Jews we don't want anymore.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We don't want these refugees that were supposed to go to Cuba.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Let Cuba take them, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[SIGH]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was almost a week, actually, that we were there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we sailed along the Florida coast, I think, for about three days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember-- this is interesting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, I remember this vividly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father and I were standing on the deck, and it was dusk and I was-- we were looking towards shore.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember seeing lights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said to my father, what are those lights?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said to me, oh, that's an American city called Miami.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And of course, Miami could have been on the moon for all-- for for all the good it did us, because there was no way we could get there, nor did we get there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The thing is, I've been in Miami many times since I've been in the United States.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when I walk along the beach and I look out towards the ocean, I always get this-- this strange feeling, because then coming to Miami was, you know, was an impossibility.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
